description:
Expand your track list with the Best of 80's Vol.1 Song Pack! You need the full game Let's Sing Country to use this DLC. Includes hit songs:
• Tears for Fears "Everybody Wants To Rule The World"
• Dexy's Midnight Runners "Come On Eileen"
• Lionel Richie "All Night Long"
• Soft Cell "Tainted Love"
• Elton John "Sacrifice"
name: Let's Sing - Best of 80's Vol. 1 Song Pack
